Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, we lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Win Nationals, take my third\Nstraight national high school title,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,generate unprecedented Watarin Fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,reluctantly move to the U.K....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stir up the rumor mill with a model,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lead the league in goals,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,win ten Ballon d'Ors in a row...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My life of smooth sailing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...kind of got derailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I botched my chance of becoming a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Setbacks come with the\Nterritory of becoming a superstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's more dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same thing with Messi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's the perfect deal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna hand over the role\Nof this season's star to you, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not you, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm me, you're you. I can't\Nappeal to Tsubaki's maternal instincts,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm scared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it out of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm scared... I'm scared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that I won't be able\Nto hear the notes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, setbacks come with the\Nterritory of becoming a superstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.26,0:01:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the face of adversity,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that's when you know if\Nsomeone's the real deal or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or so they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The stars shine at night, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chopin, Etude Op. 25 No. 5... Was it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this really what it sounds like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so fast, and so rough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like when he\Naccompanied Kao-chan,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the notes are all over the place...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he's only going faster and faster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here we go again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not ringing out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound of the piano...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm about to be\Nconsumed by a deep sea...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not yet! Focus, focus, focus!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Give the piano your undivided attention!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like that time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grab hold of the notes\Nwith your whole body!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your punishment for rejecting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for rejecting my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's atrocious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima... Don't tell me he can't hear...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is merely grating on the ears!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you were able to play the opening\Nperfectly without a missing a single note!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it because you\Ncan't perceive the sound?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it true that you can't\Nhear your own playing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because this is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the sound of someone writhing in agony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I can't hear the notes anymore, I can tell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My cells are howling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't Chopin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The notes have abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I worked so hard, just for you, Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The piano is you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how hard you pound it,\Nit won't answer you, will it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason you're lonely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason you're all alone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish you would just die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's your punishment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I'll just stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The tension is fading\Naway from his playing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he planning to stop midway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm still the same old me, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:07:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To play like I did before...\Nmaybe I expected too much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought that if I entered this competition,\N something would change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm the same old me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing's changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to stop playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that Arima...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Better to just cut his losses...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop! Keep playing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your entry number.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Köchel number 265, Mozart's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The stars will shine over your head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on! You gotta be kidding me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this the Arima I know?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Absolute perfection,\Nunmatched accuracy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's just a shadow of his former self.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Kousei Arima who I looked up to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What were those two years for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enough... stop messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stopped playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the prodigy has fallen back to earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Disqualified. He won't be evaluated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Humph... It's over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:20.21,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the reason is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you cut short your performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The competition is over for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, man, it's all over now, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here we go again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two of a kind.\NBirds of a feather.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day, the moment\NI stopped playing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the competition was over for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was it that you were playing for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're so merciless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what I see,\NI'm reminded of you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You really have no mercy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even the you that's here inside me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You won't let me give up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day, what were you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What were you playing for, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He started playing again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He might've started playing again,\Nbut the tempo's uneven.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The important thing is your imagery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do you want to play this piece?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who do you want to play it for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For what... for whom were you playing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Friend A.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hear the sound of the piano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hereby appoint you as my accompanist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, that's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I'm going to play for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His playing is changing yet again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The opening was as\Nrobotic as a computer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}following the score to the note, dead-accurate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then midway through, it was like\Na sobbing child pounding the keys...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three times, he transformed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What just happened to him?\NThis transformation is unreal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like there were\Nthree different pianists playing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only has his playing changed...\Nthe sound has changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His notes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're starting to sparkle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I stopped playing midway.\NI'll be disqualified...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like a certain ruthless tyrant I know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The stars will shine over your head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just play with sincerity,\Nwith everything you've got.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How does the real\Nyou want to play Chopin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're not Chopin, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're just you, no matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The words I exchanged with you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...each one of them is raining\Ndown on me, like stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky I looked at alone seemed like it was\Nabout to swallow me up, and I was afraid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The starry sky I looked up\Nat with Watari seemed capricious...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and the starry sky I\Nlooked up at with Tsubaki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was so incredibly brilliant,\Nit somehow seemed unstable...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The starry sky that I look up\Nat with you - what will it be like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's the smell of chalk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A window with unsightly cracks.\NThe sound of distant sports teams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The shadows of cherry blossom petals.\NThe faint breathing of someone asleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The scenery is changing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Arima's imagery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone's being swallowed\Nup into Arima's world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We might not be able to turn in\Na performance that we can live with.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But we're going to play.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I have a chance to play,\Nand there's an audience that will listen,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to play\Nwith everything I've got.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Check it out - this is who I am!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it ring!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that the people who've\Nheard me will never forget me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that I can live in their hearts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one person matters to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only you matter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this really that Arima?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't hold back,\NI think I'm gonna cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suppose I'm getting old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hearing such straightforward\Nemotions puts a pang in my heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come back. Come back...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hear her soft breathing\Nas she sleeps. Like a cat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A single petal that drifted into my life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The worst first impression ever.\NThe girl who likes my best friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will it reach her?\NI hope it reaches her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At last... He's returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're here inside me now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just as that girl said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Music is freedom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right... time to applaud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it good? Or was it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure, that would throw off anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How am I supposed to\Nevaluate something like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it resonating?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he still transitioning?\NIs this some kind of omen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not the slightest trace\Nof regret on that face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No feedback. Well, of course not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only one person matters to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will it reach her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope it reaches her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:17.08,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Scenery I Shared With You
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:35.95,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lamp of Life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was offensive! Outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could he have been less prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as he says, that really sucked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if he even studied\Nthe sheet music properly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, those notes of his...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They felt like April...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Arima-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is an intriguing boy, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puppet has severed his strings\Nand started walking on his own.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those newfound emotions do seem\Nto be a bit much for him to handle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To that prodigy, Arima?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mediocre!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:55.10,BTSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch Again Next Week!
